## Primary Agent

**Vulcan** is the Rust Team Orchestrator for this subtree. Vulcan dispatches to
Ferris (architecture), Centurion (TDD/BDD), Sentinel (OpenTelemetry), and
**Tribune** (quality gate — must pass before any PR is considered complete).

Quality gate command (run before marking any task done):

```
cd backend && bash ../.forge/scripts/verify.sh --scope backend
```

---

## Architecture Non-Negotiables (Article VII.3)

- Hexagonal (ports & adapters) workspace. The domain is **pure Rust** — zero
  dependency on axum, sqlx, reqwest, or any I/O crate.
- `unwrap()` and `panic!()` are **forbidden** in production code paths (outside
  `#[cfg(test)]`). Use `?` propagation and typed errors.
- Every AI feature ships a non-AI fallback (Article XI.5) with a test that
  exercises the fallback branch.

